name: LoginWars2
description: An alternative launcher for Guild Wars 2 with support for multiple accounts and some extra cheese.

releases.name: v1.3.0
releases.body:
## Changelog
- Update dependencies
- Change the update system, instead of using my updates.kasoki.de thingy it now relies completely on Githubs "Releases" system

releases.name: v1.2.0
releases.body:
## Changelog
- Upgrade Electron to v1.3.2, should improve performance, stability etc.

releases.name: v1.1.1
releases.body:
## Changelog
- Add new Daily view ( #15 ) which has a lot more informations like tomorrows dailies and fractal dailies
- Update to Electron 0.37.6
- Fix a display bug with Dailies

releases.name: v0.9.5
releases.body:
### Changelog
- add server flags to presentation mode
- Improve app pin behaviour

releases.name: v0.9.4
releases.body:
### Changelog
- Small bug fix which was basically a typo
- Update Electron to 0.34.4

### Changelog from 0.9.3
- Add ability to detect server location [eu, na] interesting for #8 
- Show small indicator icon for server location/language (NA servers always show the US flag however for EU servers it shows either the language of the server or the EU flag for english servers)

### Changelog from 0.9.2
- Change some odd colors

### Changelog from 0.9.1
- Log into .log files instead of localStorage, fix #14 
- Add logs for main thread

### Changelog from 0.9.0
- Add indicator for new trades, fix #11 
- Reduce font size in Daily tab
- Add ability to select custom paths, fix #13

releases.name: v0.8.1
releases.body:
### Changelog
- Small bug fix that killed the entire app

### Changelog from 0.8.0
- Add support for the new 64bit GW2 client

**Note**: You can now see which executable (Gw2 executable) Login Wars 2 is using in the "Settings" dialog.

releases.name: v0.8.0

**Note**: You can now see which executable (Gw2 executable) Login Wars 2 is using in the "Settings" dialog.

releases.name: v0.7.0
releases.body:
### Changelog
- Add new logger
- Add ability to show rank icons instead of the account icon if you've granted pvp permission
- Slight improvements to account dialogs

releases.name: v0.6.0
releases.body:
### Changelog
- Add small error badge beside account name when something went wrong with the API connection
- Open debug window in a new window by default

releases.name: v0.5.4
releases.body:
### Changelog
- Improve drag behaviour to act more like a titlebar (most people didn't like the drag everywhere thing)
- Slight improvements in the appearance of presentation mode. The mails look now a lot more natural
- Update to Electron 0.34.1
